Package registry.Nodes

Class KeyNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • registry.Nodes.KeyNode
  • public class KeyNode
extends java.lang.Object
    Wraps a key (NK) cell Uses lazy evaluation - child nodes and values will only be loaded if queried
